"title": "5325: gifts",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5325: gifts",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Presents, given freely and without payment. Scripture lays considerable emphasis on salvation as a gift given by God to sinful, undeserving men and women.</p>\n<h2>Gifts given by God</h2>\n<h3>His one and only Son, Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:14-2Cor9:15\">2CO 9:14–9:15</a></p>\n<h3>Salvation and eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:10\">JHN 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12-Rom5:17\">ROM 5:12–5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:25-Rom11:32\">ROM 11:25–11:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:7\">1PE 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:17\">REV 22:17</a></p>\n<h3>Grace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8-Eph2:9\">EPH 2:8–2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:8-2Cor9:11\">2CO 9:8–9:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:14-2Cor9:15\">2CO 9:14–9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:7\">EPH 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:7-Eph4:8\">EPH 4:7–4:8</a></p>\n<h3>Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:13\">LUK 11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:4\">ACT 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:18\">ACT 8:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:44\">ACT 10:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:15\">ACT 11:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4\">HEB 6:4</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual gifts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:1-1Cor12:11\">1CO 12:1–12:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:4-Rom12:8\">ROM 12:4–12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:4-1Cor1:7\">1CO 1:4–1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:27-1Cor12:31\">1CO 12:27–12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:2\">1CO 13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:1\">1CO 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:14\">1TI 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:6\">2TI 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:4\">HEB 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:10\">1PE 4:10</a></p>\n<h3>Other gifts from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:17\">JAS 1:17</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:20\">GEN 30:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:27\">1SA 1:27</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5\">JAS 1:5</a> <em>wisdom</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:1-1Cor7:7\">1CO 7:1–7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:13\">ECC 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:19\">ECC 5:19</a></p>\n<h2>Gifts given to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:18\">PSA 68:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:3\">NUM 7:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:9\">NUM 18:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:52\">NUM 31:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:11\">DEU 12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:16-Deut16:17\">DEU 16:16–16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:12-2Chr31:14\">2CH 31:12–31:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:29\">PSA 68:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps76:11\">PSA 76:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa18:7\">ISA 18:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:39\">EZK 20:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:23-Matt5:24\">MAT 5:23–5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:3-Matt15:6\">MAT 15:3–15:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:9-Mark7:13\">MRK 7:9–7:13</a> <em>condemnation concerning the Corban oath</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:1-Luke21:4\">LUK 21:1–21:4</a></p>\n<h2>Gifts given to false gods</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:38\">DAN 11:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:25-Ezek20:26\">EZK 20:25–20:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:30-Ezek20:31\">EZK 20:30–20:31</a></p>\n<h2>Gifts given by kings</h2>\n<h3>To their subjects</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:18\">EST 2:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:19\">2SA 6:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:2-1Chr16:3\">1CH 16:2–16:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:8\">2SA 11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:16-Ezek46:17\">EZK 46:16–46:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:6\">DAN 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:48\">DAN 2:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:13-Dan5:17\">DAN 5:13–5:17</a></p>\n<h3>To other kings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:8\">2KI 16:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:18-1Kgs15:19\">1KI 15:18–15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:17-2Kgs12:18\">2KI 12:17–12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:12\">2KI 20:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa39:1\">ISA 39:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:10\">PSA 72:10</a></p>\n<h2>Gifts given to kings</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:11\">2CH 17:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:27\">1SA 10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:25\">1KI 10:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:24\">2CH 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:5\">2CH 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:23\">2CH 32:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:23\">ISA 1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:3\">MIC 7:3</a></p>\n<h2>Gifts given to the poor and needy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:29-Acts11:30\">ACT 11:29–11:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:20-Esth9:22\">EST 9:20–9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:9\">PSA 112:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:4\">ACT 10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:17\">ACT 24:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:1-1Cor16:3\">1CO 16:1–16:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:16-2Cor8:21\">2CO 8:16–8:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:5\">2CO 9:5</a></p>\n<h2>Gifts given by fathers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:6\">GEN 25:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:7-Matt7:11\">MAT 7:7–7:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:9-Luke11:13\">LUK 11:9–11:13</a></p>\n<h2>Gifts given at marriage</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:16\">1KI 9:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:53\">GEN 24:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:11-Gen34:12\">GEN 34:11–34:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:16-Exod22:17\">EXO 22:16–22:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:28-Deut22:29\">DEU 22:28–22:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:24-1Sam18:27\">1SA 18:24–18:27</a></p>\n<h2>Gifts given to assuage anger</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:14\">PRO 21:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:13-Gen32:21\">GEN 32:13–32:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:1-Gen43:26\">GEN 43:1–43:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:4-1Sam25:35\">1SA 25:4–25:35</a></p>",
